item.title: About
item.description: This theme was made with Hugo v0.17 on a Mac. It was coded mostly using Textmate and Firefox. It includes a number of features that will help a developer create and manage websites. Responsive design mobile ready Custom CSS ability Pre defined archetypes Markdown To install this theme you need to download the latest version of Hugo from their website. Follow the instructions to install and configure Hugo for your system.
